Name: ClickCells: Office Lady
About the game: Erotic comic book puzzle! What does a girl do when she is left alone? You can find out if you go through ClickCells to the end! In the game you have to solve puzzles with multi-colored cubes. Your task is to destroy all the orange cubes, and deliver the blue to the platform, and in between the levels enjoy the images of a beautiful naked girl. Also by numerous requests in the game appeared 'administrator mode'. Administrator mode Press the F button while at the art or puzzle level and you will immediately open the entire block of five puzzles and get the corresponding achievements. There's a game waiting for you Interesting puzzles A comic book from LeArtNi Nice music from Trauerbaum Beautiful achievements Powered by Clickteam Fusion 2.5
